District Court for the District of Delaware found that the two patents on Cinvanti, which</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174197278/image_174197278.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742131-relief-for-heron-therapeutics-after-the-court-win-on-cinvanti", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 23:01:27"}, {"id": "4742079", "title": "Hormel Foods: Bears Strike Yet Another Blow", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365382318/image_1365382318.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Grilled Spam Burger with Fries\" data-id=\"1365382318\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365382318/image_1365382318.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365382318/image_1365382318.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365382318/image_1365382318.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365382318/image_1365382318.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365382318/image_1365382318.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365382318/image_1365382318.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365382318/image_1365382318.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365382318/image_1365382318.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">LauriPatterson</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>We have generally stayed away from the bullish view that has gripped investors about Hormel Foods Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HRL\" title=\"Hormel Foods Corporation\">HRL</a></span>). Granted, as the stock has moved lower we have looked for some tactical upside plays. But overall, we saw it as a stock with</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365382318/image_1365382318.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742079-hormel-foods-bears-strike-yet-another-blow", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 22:45:09"}, {"id": "4742125", "title": "LendingClub: Too Early To Downgrade", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1179464837/image_1179464837.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"LendingClub headquarters in Silicon Valley.\" data-id=\"1179464837\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1179464837/image_1179464837.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1179464837/image_1179464837.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1179464837/image_1179464837.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1179464837/image_1179464837.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1179464837/image_1179464837.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1179464837/image_1179464837.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1179464837/image_1179464837.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1179464837/image_1179464837.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36p